	<blockquote>
		<p class="cite">For the first time in&nbsp;human history, we&nbsp;can do&nbsp;more than just gaze at&nbsp;the stars. We&nbsp;can actually reach them.</p>
	</blockquote>
	<p class="author">Yuri Milner</p>

